00:02:22,620 --> 00:02:25,180
the Wenping Lighthouse in Weihai, right?

4
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:26,430
Yes, this is it.

5
00:02:29,079 --> 00:02:30,000
It feels really different

6
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,800
from the sea back in my hometown.

7
00:02:33,310 --> 00:02:34,500
You haven't visited your hometown

8
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:36,630
since you came back to China this time?

9
00:02:41,260 --> 00:02:43,280
So compared to the sea in your hometown,

10
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,030
how is it?

11
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,470
They're both nice.

12
00:02:46,530 --> 00:02:48,520
It just feels different.

13
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,960
The sea in my hometown is beautiful too.

14
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,520
The beach there—

15
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,910
the sand is fine, soft,

16
00:02:55,150 --> 00:02:56,120
and golden.

17
00:02:59,430 --> 00:03:00,650
What you just said

18
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:02,000
sounds familiar.

19
00:03:02,850 --> 00:03:05,050
I think I've heard it somewhere before.

20
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:07,520
Oh, right.

21
00:03:08,150 --> 00:03:09,100
There was someone

22
00:03:09,100 --> 00:03:11,100
who said the exact same thing as you.

23
00:03:11,170 --> 00:03:12,120
Really?

24
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:14,010
What a coincidence.

25
00:03:25,910 --> 00:03:26,470
Hello?

26
00:03:29,470 --> 00:03:30,680
Yes, it's me.

27
00:03:32,250 --> 00:03:34,100
[The ever-flowing time]

28
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:37,030
[is but a collection of lonely sighs.]

29
00:03:37,350 --> 00:03:40,340
[Episode 15: Pearl]

30
00:04:25,170 --> 00:04:26,680
You fool!

31
00:04:29,390 --> 00:04:30,600
Let me tell you!

32
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:33,690
You never needed to run from the start!

33
00:04:34,230 --> 00:04:37,330
It was me who killed Ni Xiangdong!

34
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:06,100
Xiaojun.

35
00:05:09,430 --> 00:05:10,360
Xiaojun.

36
00:05:13,090 --> 00:05:16,150
What are we doing?

37
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:29,830
What?

38
00:05:30,940 --> 00:05:32,430
You... You...

39
00:05:34,070 --> 00:05:36,340
You're...

40
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:39,190
the rubber factory worker,

41
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:42,600
Xu...

42
00:05:43,870 --> 00:05:44,600
Xu...

43
00:05:45,870 --> 00:05:46,600
Qing...

44
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,360
Li.

45
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,600
Where's Tianbao?

46
00:06:00,370 --> 00:06:02,710
Why would I ever harm Tianbao?

47
00:06:06,330 --> 00:06:07,090
Don't worry.

48
00:06:10,390 --> 00:06:12,360
Pier No. 3.

49
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:15,360
10 p.m.

50
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:19,870
Run.

51
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,040
Bro.

52
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,800
Make it quick for me.

53
00:06:44,420 --> 00:06:45,340
I wonder...

54
00:06:48,390 --> 00:06:51,159
if this would qualify for the insurance.

55
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,390
Hello.

56
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:07,490
This is Ni Xiangdong.

57
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,420
I'm turning myself in.

58
00:08:38,450 --> 00:08:42,280
