59
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,870
Fireworks!

60
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:46,150
So beautiful!

61
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,680
Fireworks!

62
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:49,440
♪ She's silent ♪

63
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:51,240
They're setting off fireworks!

64
00:08:51,510 --> 00:08:53,150
Fireworks! Fireworks!

65
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:55,240
Fireworks! Fireworks!

66
00:08:56,900 --> 00:09:05,880
♪ Rising in the dark night ♪

67
00:09:06,190 --> 00:09:12,490
♪ You're going far away ♪

68
00:09:15,940 --> 00:09:17,420
[For hospital discharge and transfer]

69
00:09:17,420 --> 00:09:20,820
[Two-way Referral, Public Welfare Rescue]

70
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:39,100
♪ That's the starting point of happiness ♪

71
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:46,040
♪ In the silence, I recall ♪

72
00:09:48,770 --> 00:09:57,760
♪ The bygone years of childhood ♪

73
00:09:58,090 --> 00:10:04,530
♪ The sorrow painted in black ♪

74
