Tianbao!

75
00:10:06,250 --> 00:10:07,350
Uncle Ni!

76
00:10:08,640 --> 00:10:09,560
Tianbao!

77
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:13,400
Were the fireworks beautiful?

78
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:14,600
Yes, very beautiful!

79
00:10:15,580 --> 00:10:16,670
Listen to me.

80
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,780
You must take good care of your health!

81
00:10:18,780 --> 00:10:20,050
You must be strong!

82
00:10:20,160 --> 00:10:20,850
You must study hard!

83
00:10:20,850 --> 00:10:21,540
[Police]

84
00:10:21,540 --> 00:10:22,900
You must live a good life, okay?

85
00:10:22,900 --> 00:10:23,240
Okay.

86
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,120
Police! Freeze!

87
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:24,720
Police!

88
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:26,050
-Hands up!
-What are you doing?

89
00:10:26,050 --> 00:10:26,880
-Hands up!
-Tianbao, don't be afraid!

90
00:10:26,880 --> 00:10:27,550
What are you doing?

91
00:10:27,550 --> 00:10:28,440
Don't be scared, Tianbao!

92
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,240
It's okay!

93
00:10:29,870 --> 00:10:30,410
Come. Come.

94
00:10:30,410 --> 00:10:31,810
Let Uncle Ni go!

95
00:10:31,870 --> 00:10:33,360
-Uncle Ni!
-It's okay!

96
00:10:33,670 --> 00:10:34,950
Tianbao, it's okay!

97
00:10:34,950 --> 00:10:35,470
♪ You and I didn't get it ♪

98
00:10:35,470 --> 00:10:37,220
Listen to the police officers!

99
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:37,890
Uncle Ni!

100
00:10:37,910 --> 00:10:39,290
-Go with the police officers!
-Move!

101
00:10:39,290 --> 00:10:40,080
Uncle Ni!

102
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:41,680
Release Uncle Ni!

103
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,130
Wait for me to come out!

104
00:10:43,810 --> 00:10:43,870
[Police]

105
00:10:43,870 --> 00:10:44,140
I'll come play with you again!

106
00:10:44,140 --> 00:10:46,150
♪ Naive dreams ♪

107
00:10:46,150 --> 00:10:47,630
Uncle Ni!

108
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:49,280
-Tianbao!
-Be good.

109
00:10:49,450 --> 00:10:50,980
Will you listen to Uncle Ni?

110
00:10:51,550 --> 00:10:52,280
Uncle Ni said
you should listen to the police officers.

111
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:53,390
♪ The grey night mist
drifts far and wide ♪

112
00:10:53,390 --> 00:10:55,190
Your name is Cao Tianbao, right?

113
00:10:55,270 --> 00:10:55,830
Yes.

114
00:10:57,670 --> 00:11:00,200
Would you like to talk to your mom
on the phone?

115
00:11:01,550 --> 00:11:09,150
♪ Tears glimmer softly in my eyes ♪

116
00:11:09,150 --> 00:11:09,600
Mom.

117
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:12,790
♪ The coldness has surrounded us ♪

118
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:13,600
Tianbao?

119
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:15,570
Tianbao, where are you now?

120
00:11:15,570 --> 00:11:16,700
I'm on the mountain.

121
00:11:16,790 --> 00:11:18,250
I just watched fireworks.

122
00:11:18,550 --> 00:11:18,810
Uncle Ni said

123
00:11:18,810 --> 00:11:19,550
♪ You silently ♪

124
00:11:19,550 --> 00:11:21,440
that was a gift he gave me.

125
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:22,750
Tianbao.

126
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:24,810
Uncle Ni has been arrested.

127
00:11:24,910 --> 00:11:25,410
Mom,

128
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,900
talk to the police officers now.

129
00:11:26,900 --> 00:11:28,920
♪ Disappeared in the cold fog ♪

130
00:11:28,920 --> 00:11:29,670
Chu Xiao.

131
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:32,200
Take her back to the station.

132
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:34,010
Go, sweetie. Go.

133
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:36,510
♪ Gone forever ♪

134
00:11:36,510 --> 00:11:37,630
Let's go back to the station.

135
00:11:37,630 --> 00:11:38,120
Okay.

136
00:11:45,430 --> 00:11:49,150
[Rescuing Room]

137
00:12:14,050 --> 00:12:17,300
[Rescuing Room]

138
00:12:41,090 --> 00:12:41,750
Captain Ma.

139
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:45,060
[Operating Room]

140
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:46,180
Tong.

141
00:12:46,180 --> 00:12:46,570
[Quiet]

142
00:12:46,570 --> 00:12:46,670
[Building 4 elevator]

143
00:12:46,670 --> 00:12:47,330
Captain Ma.

144
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:48,510
What did the doctor say?

145
00:12:48,510 --> 00:12:49,170
Not out yet.

146
00:12:49,270 --> 00:12:50,730
The doctor told us to wait.

147
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:06,140
Alright, alright.

148
00:13:06,790 --> 00:13:07,240
Get up.

149
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,150
It's fine.

150
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:26,160
Don't feel burdened.

151
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:29,550
Cops always...

152
00:13:31,030 --> 00:13:32,290
face things like this.

153
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:35,200
Don't look like a defeated rooster.

154
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,240
Have you called

155
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,370
Meng Zhao's mother?

156
00:13:43,270 --> 00:13:43,930
Gengsheng.

157
00:13:44,040 --> 00:13:45,000
[Building 4 elevator]

158
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,200
Notify Meng's mother.

159
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:46,750
Okay.

160
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:50,360
I'll go make the call.

161
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,620
Break it to her gently.

162
00:13:57,880 --> 00:13:59,010
It's okay. Go ahead.

163
00:14:01,270 --> 00:14:02,400
Okay, I understand.

164
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:03,800
I'm heading back now.

165
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:04,800
That's it.

166
00:14:06,550 --> 00:14:07,840
There's a situation
with the interrogation.

167
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:09,570
I need to go back to the station.

168
00:14:10,740 --> 00:14:12,340
I... I'll go too, Captain Ma.

169
00:14:14,630 --> 00:14:15,490
I can handle it.

170
00:14:21,550 --> 00:14:21,780
You're saying

171
00:14:21,780 --> 00:14:22,510
[Guanhai Branch,
Weihai Municipal Public Security Bureau]

172
00:14:22,510 --> 00:14:24,360
you saw Cao Xiaojun and Wu Ximei

173
00:14:24,380 --> 00:14:24,650
burying Ni Xiangdong, right?

174
00:14:24,650 --> 00:14:26,660
[Interrogation Room 1]

175
00:14:26,660 --> 00:14:27,260
Yes.

176
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:28,850
After you dug him up,

177
00:14:28,870 --> 00:14:29,600
was he alive

178
00:14:29,630 --> 00:14:30,320
or dead?

179
00:14:32,140 --> 00:14:32,840
Dead.

180
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:34,120
Describe

181
00:14:34,150 --> 00:14:35,610
the condition of the body.

182
00:14:38,550 --> 00:14:39,440
The body...

183
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:41,640
was covered in blood.

184
00:14:43,140 --> 00:14:45,670
His stomach
had been stabbed multiple times,

185
00:14:47,270 --> 00:14:49,800
and his face was smashed
beyond recognition.

186
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:51,330
Can you explain

187
00:14:51,360 --> 00:14:52,480
how Ni Xiangdong's body

188
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,320
ended up

189
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:55,320
in your coffin?

190
00:15:00,010 --> 00:15:02,140
You've seen this photo before, right?

191
00:15:03,870 --> 00:15:05,080
Who took this photo?

192
00:15:07,550 --> 00:15:08,510
Do you know who was

193
00:15:08,510 --> 00:15:09,510
in the box?

194
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:14,120
You and Cao Xiaojun

195
00:15:14,150 --> 00:15:15,210
asked Ni Xiangdong

196
00:15:15,270 --> 00:15:16,600
to carry the box up the mountain.

197
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:17,600
If you didn't

198
00:15:17,630 --> 00:15:18,440
take this photo,

199
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:19,300
who did?

200
00:15:25,700 --> 00:15:27,320
[January 4, 2011]

201
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:28,720
Wu Ximei, let me tell you.

202
00:15:28,750 --> 00:15:30,620
Stalling for time now

203
00:15:30,670 --> 00:15:32,530
is completely pointless for you.

204
00:15:36,030 --> 00:15:37,030
Where is Tianbao?

205
00:15:41,550 --> 00:15:42,210
Captain Ma.

206
00:15:42,790 --> 00:15:44,250
How's it going over there?

207
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:45,960
She keeps looking at the clock.

208
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:47,080
She must be up to something,

209
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:49,010
but I can't figure it out right now.

210
00:15:49,510 --> 00:15:50,600
Xu Qingli said

211
00:15:50,670 --> 00:15:51,290
back then,

212
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:52,580
he saw with his own eyes

213
00:15:52,630 --> 00:15:54,490
the entire process of Cao Xiaojun

214
00:15:54,550 --> 00:15:56,910
and Wu Ximei burying Ni Xiangdong's body.

215
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:58,510
Ni Xiangdong's body

216
00:15:58,510 --> 00:15:59,360
had multiple stab wounds

217
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:00,220
in the abdomen,

218
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:01,840
and his face was smashed.

219
00:16:01,910 --> 00:16:03,710
So we need to focus on finding out

220
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:05,300
the specific state

221
00:16:05,590 --> 00:16:06,920
of Ni Xiangdong's death

222
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:08,670
and the exact burial site.

223
00:16:09,110 --> 00:16:09,480
Okay.

224
00:16:09,550 --> 00:16:09,910
Go.

225
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:10,390
Yes.

226
00:16:12,290 --> 00:16:16,260
[January 4, 2011]

227
00:16:17,430 --> 00:16:18,720
Since you already know everything,

228
00:16:18,720 --> 00:16:20,600
just sentence me as you see fit.

229
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:22,620
Why bother interrogating me?

230
00:16:22,750 --> 00:16:23,910
Having you confess

231
00:16:24,470 --> 00:16:25,670
is giving you a chance

232
00:16:25,720 --> 00:16:26,910
for leniency.

233
00:16:29,820 --> 00:16:31,480
Fine, I'll talk.

234
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:37,270
Can you promise

235
00:16:37,510 --> 00:16:39,710
that you won't tell Tianbao about this?

236
00:16:40,790 --> 00:16:41,320
Yes.

237
00:16:46,390 --> 00:16:47,390
At that time,

238
00:16:49,280 --> 00:16:51,740
Ni Xiangdong was already addicted
to drugs.

239
00:16:54,740 --> 00:16:56,200
He often didn't come home,

240
00:16:58,670 --> 00:17:00,600
and his moods were unpredictable.

241
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:03,270
One night he came home

242
00:17:03,720 --> 00:17:05,119
and suddenly went crazy,

243
00:17:05,880 --> 00:17:09,339
saying he wanted to find his gun
to settle a score with someone.

244
00:17:10,010 --> 00:17:11,470
Where's my five-shooter?

245
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:14,060
I tried to stop him.

246
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:17,579
When I tried to stop him, he...

247
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:20,109
pinned me down on the bed

248
00:17:20,109 --> 00:17:21,440
and started choking me.

249
00:17:22,300 --> 00:17:23,490
I'll kill you!

250
00:17:24,589 --> 00:17:26,250
Xiaojun came over to stop him.

251
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:30,850
He stabbed him once in the back.

252
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:37,830
Ni Xiangdong...

253
00:17:38,350 --> 00:17:39,830
kicked Xiaojun away

254
00:17:44,550 --> 00:17:46,010
and continued choking me.

255
00:17:47,230 --> 00:17:48,690
I was choked unconscious.

256
00:17:49,750 --> 00:17:50,750
When I regained consciousness,

257
00:17:50,750 --> 00:17:52,560
I saw Xiaojun and Ni Xiangdong

258
00:17:52,590 --> 00:17:53,680
lying on the floor.

259
00:17:54,880 --> 00:17:56,640
I went to check on them

260
00:17:58,110 --> 00:18:00,480
and found Ni Xiangdong was already dead.

261
00:18:01,240 --> 00:18:03,170
Are you sure he was dead at the time?

262
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:06,860
His stomach was covered in blood.

263
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:09,370
Other than the wounds...

264
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:10,790
on his stomach and back,

265
00:18:10,810 --> 00:18:12,670
were there wounds anywhere else?

266
00:18:14,310 --> 00:18:15,030
No.

267
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:18,350
None at all?

268
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:19,750
No.

269
00:18:22,190 --> 00:18:22,930
Alone,

270
00:18:22,960 --> 00:18:24,690
I couldn't handle both of them.

271
00:18:26,250 --> 00:18:27,310
So I thought of a way

272
00:18:27,310 --> 00:18:28,640
to separate them.

273
00:18:30,350 --> 00:18:33,010
Whoever
went to the Chengxi construction site,

274
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:35,640
it would buy me some time.

275
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:38,050
I just wanted to talk to either of them,

276
00:18:38,050 --> 00:18:39,030
whether it was Cao Xiaojun

277
00:18:39,030 --> 00:18:39,880
or Wu Ximei.

278
00:18:40,110 --> 00:18:41,240
Either one would do.

279
00:18:41,620 --> 00:18:42,480
I just wanted

280
00:18:42,510 --> 00:18:44,000
to have a proper talk with them.

281
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:45,120
I told him,

282
00:18:45,550 --> 00:18:46,920
"I didn't do anything.

283
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,460
Why do you want to kill me?"

284
00:18:49,070 --> 00:18:50,800
Then he suddenly got agitated.

285
00:18:51,870 --> 00:18:53,330
He stabbed me with a knife.

286
00:18:55,000 --> 00:18:56,330
I could only fight back.

287
00:18:59,550 --> 00:19:01,200
Then I grabbed a rock

288
00:19:01,270 --> 00:19:02,270
in self-defense.

289
00:19:02,830 --> 00:19:04,110
It's not up to you to decide

290
00:19:04,110 --> 00:19:05,350
if it was self-defense or not.

291
00:19:05,350 --> 00:19:07,630
We determine that.

292
00:19:08,160 --> 00:19:09,070
But I hope you

