00:24:28,270 --> 00:24:29,200
What's going on?

412
00:24:29,400 --> 00:24:30,330
What's going on?

413
00:24:36,070 --> 00:24:36,870
Captain Meng!

414
00:24:40,750 --> 00:24:41,590
Captain Meng!

415
00:24:41,680 --> 00:24:42,730
Meng!

416
00:24:43,680 --> 00:24:44,660
Meng!

