00:24:51,740 --> 00:24:52,160
[Iron-blooded Police Spirit]

420
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:53,750
Actually, Meng Zhao is aware

421
00:24:53,750 --> 00:24:54,950
that behind his back,

422
00:24:54,960 --> 00:24:55,790
people say

