00:24:59,350 --> 00:25:00,350
He knows very well

427
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:02,510
how fragile human life is.

428
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,750
He doesn't want anyone

429
00:25:05,920 --> 00:25:07,850
