445
00:25:37,240 --> 00:25:37,720
It could also

446
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:39,520
cost your comrades their lives.

447
00:25:42,330 --> 00:25:42,920
Captain Ma.

448
00:25:42,920 --> 00:25:43,480
Xia.

449
00:25:44,320 --> 00:25:45,720
