451
00:25:46,230 --> 00:25:47,240
The DNA from the body

452
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:47,830
in Nanyang

453
00:25:47,830 --> 00:25:49,350
has been compared with Cao Tianbao's.

454
00:25:49,350 --> 00:25:50,190
We can confirm it's

455
00:25:50,190 --> 00:25:52,120
Cao Tianbao's biological father.

456
00:25:52,160 --> 00:25:53,180
The direct cause of Cao Xiaojun's death

457
00:25:53,180 --> 00:25:54,400
