458
00:25:54,400 --> 00:25:56,070
Blunt force trauma to the head,
multiple strikes.

459
00:25:56,070 --> 00:25:57,160
Additionally, the left ear is missing.

460
00:25:57,160 --> 00:25:58,560
The rest is in the report.

461
00:25:58,790 --> 00:25:59,480
And the complete autopsy report

462
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:00,310
on Liu Cheng'an

463
00:26:00,310 --> 00:26:01,110
is out as well.

464
00:26:01,200 --> 00:26:02,110
We found stone fragments

465
00:26:02,110 --> 00:26:02,960
in the wounds.

466
00:26:03,310 --> 00:26:04,160
Therefore, I think

467
00:26:04,160 --> 00:26:04,920
that before his death,

468
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:06,550
he was violently struck on the head

469
00:26:06,550 --> 00:26:07,510
at least 3 to 4 times

470
00:26:07,510 --> 00:26:09,640
with the sharp edge of a mountain rock.

471
00:26:10,200 --> 00:26:11,380
This is Cao Xiaojun's.

472
00:26:11,380 --> 00:26:12,380
You might need it.

473
00:26:12,880 --> 00:26:13,410
Tong Hao.

474
00:26:15,720 --> 00:26:16,850
Go run a comparison.

