00:26:17,880 --> 00:26:18,880
Captain Ma, that's all.

476
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:19,240
If there's nothing else,

477
00:26:19,240 --> 00:26:19,830
I'll get back to work.

478
00:26:19,830 --> 00:26:20,510
Okay, okay.

479
00:26:21,550 --> 00:26:22,070
Xia.

480
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:28,750
Meng Zhao...

481
00:26:31,640 --> 00:26:32,750
I know...

482
00:26:32,830 --> 00:26:33,760
about Meng Zhao.

483
00:26:35,200 --> 00:26:35,930
Don't worry.

484
00:26:36,550 --> 00:26:37,270
I'm fine.

485
00:26:37,790 --> 00:26:39,160
After I finish my work,

486
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:40,960
I'll go visit him.

487
00:26:41,270 --> 00:26:42,440
Okay, okay.

