00:27:42,930 --> 00:27:44,430
[Guanhai Branch,
Weihai Municipal Public Security Bureau]

510
00:27:44,460 --> 00:27:46,780
[Guanhai Branch,
Law Enforcement Case Management Center]

511
00:27:48,830 --> 00:27:49,510
Xu Qingli.

512
00:27:52,310 --> 00:27:53,680
Regarding the case of Liu Cheng'an,

513
00:27:53,680 --> 00:27:54,940
tell us what happened.

