00:27:55,030 --> 00:27:56,160
As I told you before,

515
00:27:56,750 --> 00:27:58,550
leniency for those who confess.

516
00:28:02,400 --> 00:28:03,720
Who is Liu Cheng'an?

517
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:08,000
The security guard

518
00:28:08,070 --> 00:28:10,070
on duty that night at Mount Fufeng.

519
00:28:11,420 --> 00:28:13,020
He had no grudge against you.

520
00:28:13,070 --> 00:28:14,410
You didn't even know

521
00:28:14,440 --> 00:28:15,310
his name.

522
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:16,250
How could you

523
00:28:16,310 --> 00:28:17,170
be so ruthless?

524
00:28:19,720 --> 00:28:20,720
I didn't kill him.

525
00:28:21,350 --> 00:28:22,110
Then tell me,

526
00:28:22,200 --> 00:28:23,640
after you opened the box,

527
00:28:23,660 --> 00:28:25,070
was Liu Cheng'an, whom you saw inside,

528
00:28:25,070 --> 00:28:26,400
still breathing or not?

529
00:28:26,590 --> 00:28:27,720
Was he already dead?

530
00:28:31,480 --> 00:28:32,240
Yes.

531
00:28:32,830 --> 00:28:33,630
How did he die?

532
00:28:34,160 --> 00:28:35,260
Help me!

533
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:37,370
I don't know.

534
00:28:38,310 --> 00:28:39,840
Are you sure you don't know?

535
00:28:42,470 --> 00:28:44,510
I felt he was already dead.

536
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:46,000
Then how did

537
00:28:46,030 --> 00:28:47,110
his uniform end up on you?

538
00:28:47,110 --> 00:28:48,570
You must know that, right?

539
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:50,330
The police were coming.

540
00:28:50,830 --> 00:28:52,890
I was afraid of being checked by them,

541
00:28:53,270 --> 00:28:54,960
