565
00:29:41,240 --> 00:29:42,110
and struck

566
00:29:42,400 --> 00:29:43,240
his left forehead

567
00:29:43,240 --> 00:29:44,110
once,

568
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:44,920
again

569
00:29:45,000 --> 00:29:45,830
and again,

570
00:29:46,030 --> 00:29:47,750
