576
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:01,880
on the mountain.

577
00:30:03,030 --> 00:30:04,480
You gambled that Mount Fufeng is so vast,

578
00:30:04,480 --> 00:30:05,200
with so many rocks,

579
00:30:05,200 --> 00:30:06,930
the police would never find it.

580
00:30:08,350 --> 00:30:09,960
You gambled
that even if the police searched,

581
00:30:09,960 --> 00:30:11,480
they might eventually give up

582
00:30:11,480 --> 00:30:14,360
because the mountain is too big,
the rocks too numerous.

583
00:30:14,360 --> 00:30:15,420
But you were wrong.

584
00:30:16,110 --> 00:30:17,960
We police are best

585
00:30:19,440 --> 00:30:21,500
at unraveling clues thread by thread

586
00:30:23,790 --> 00:30:25,720
